<p class="">Has my hon. Friend heard, in his division or anywhere else, when engaged in the prosecution of his political work, any suggestion in any quarter whatever that the Prime Minister is pursuing a policy of dictatorship?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
