                Mr. Cartland
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0d3423a9-57e9-40f7-ab74-bb23023db669" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-08-02/debates/f089bef4-49c4-4ea2-b404-67419b49336b/Adjournment(Summer)#contribution-0d3423a9-57e9-40f7-ab74-bb23023db669">
