    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">That is not my fault. I want to make clear to the House my regret and disappointment that I had anything to do with his selection as a Member of Parliament for his division.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
